quran[13{c,v,t}:
43,61,Wa innahoo la'ilmul lis Saa'ati fala tamtarunna bihaa wattabi'oon; haazaa Siraatum Mustaqeem
43,62,Wa laa yasuddan nakumush Shaitaanu innahoo lakum 'aduwwum mubeen
43,63,Wa lammaa jaaa'a 'Eesaa bilbaiyinaati qaala qad ji'tukum bil Hikmati wa li-ubaiyina lakum ba'dal lazee takhtalifoona feehi fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
43,64,Innal laaha Huwa Rabbee wa Rabbukum fa'budooh; haaza Siraatum Mustaqeem
43,65,Fakhtalafal ahzaabu mim bainihim fawailul lillazeena zalamoo min 'azaabi Yawmin aleem
43,66,Hal yanzuroona illas Saa'ata an taatiyahum baghtatanw wa hum laa yash'uroon
43,67,Al akhillaaa'u Yawma'izim ba'duhum liba'din 'aduwwun illal muttaqeen�(section 6)
43,68,Yaa 'ibaadi laa khawfun 'alaikumul Yawma wa laaa antum tahzanoon
43,69,Allazeena aamanoo bi Aayaatinaa wa kaanoo muslimeen
43,70,Udkhulul Jannata antum wa azwaajukum tuhbaroon
43,71,"Yutaafu 'alaihim bishaa fim min zahabinw wa akwaab, wa feehaa maatashtaheehil anfusu wa talazzul a'yunu wa antum feehaa khaalidoon"
43,72,Wa tilkal jannatul lateee ooristumoohaa bimaa kuntum ta'maloon
43,73,Lakum feehaa faakihatun kaseeratum minhaa taakuloon
